                 <h4><strong>AIMS OF THIS PROGRAMME</strong></h4>
                 <ul>
                   <li>To prepare students for the award of Joint Higher National Diploma</li>
                   <li>As it is referred to as Joint means hands- on experience in the industry they will eventually 
                    seek employment.</li>
                   <li>To prepare students to be suitable to the demands of the sectors where they would seek immediate employment after graduation or completion of National Youth Service Corps as Junior Manager or Assistant Operations Manager in Port Complexes or Mining Sites environment.</li>
                   <li>To prepare students to be able to go on to study for the Master-In- Technology in any of these 
                    Specialism. <ul>
                      <li>Port Logistics Environment</li>
                      <li>Port & Terminal industry & Management</li>
                      <li>Mining Technology & Engineering</li>
                      <li>Petroleum Management & Marketing</li>
                      <li>Petroleum Economics & Finance</li>
