                      <li>Mining Accounting & Taxation</li>
                      <li>Mining Risk & Insurance Management</li>
                      <li>Hospitality Business & Management</li>
                      <li>Entrepreneurship & Technical Skills Acquisitions Management</li>
                      <li>Labour & Industrial Relations</li>
                      <li>Health, Safety, Environment & Occupational Health & Safety Hazards</li>
                      <li>Security, Disaster, Emergency Management, Search & Rescue</li>
                      <li>Customer Care Management</li>
                    </ul> </li>
                   <li>The Students while in session would have to spend 2-months in an economic sector of their choice that would enable them to write their term/Project papers before graduation.</li>
                   <li>Students would be expected to attend to workshop, conferences, seminars, so as to shore up their confidence and listen to experienced persons in this industry, etc.</li>
